headline: HII Expands Partnership With Babcock to Build Virginia-Class Submarine
summary: Huntington Ingalls expands its partnership with Babcock to boost Virginia-class submarine production and strengthen supply-chain resilience across U.S. and U.K. operations.

headline: Huntington Ingalls Industries (HII): Evaluating Valuation After New Defense Tech, Submarine Partnership and 3D Printing Moves
summary: Huntington Ingalls Industries (HII) has been busy on several fronts, from rolling out its GRIMM spectrum dominance system to expanding a submarine partnership with Babcock and investing in advanced metal 3D printing at Newport News.
